<span id="freeTextContainer18391263974324630716"><p>Months after his mysterious disappearance from a routine fishing trip, no one really expects over-the-hill Texas housewife Lory Latchley to find her missing husband--especially her husband. The Manufactured Identity is clinical psychologist Heath Sommer&apos;s ever-escalating immersion into the world of unlikely friends who each awaken to find their faithful companions missing </p></span>
  <span id="freeText18391263974324630716" style="display:none"><p>Months after his mysterious disappearance from a routine fishing trip, no one really expects over-the-hill Texas housewife Lory Latchley to find her missing husband--especially her husband. The Manufactured Identity is clinical psychologist Heath Sommer's ever-escalating immersion into the world of unlikely friends who each awaken to find their faithful companions missing without warning or reason. Desperate to find meaning in their pain, they are thrust by the auspices of fate into a common thread of mystery and human frailty. In the end, the fate of all may reside in the unstable hands of rookie pastor John Joe, but ultimately Lory and her newfound partners will uncover a truth so unnerving it makes even infidelity look palatable.</p></span>
  <a data-text-id="18391263974324630716" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

