<span id="freeTextContainer17140191114064777667">Really cool book. Wasn&apos;t sure where it was going for a while but in a good way, and it ended cool. Kinda sad in parts, but definitely keeps your interest. If people in the world are really like this in therapy, that&apos;s kinda creepy. Highly recommended. </span>
  <span id="freeText17140191114064777667" style="display:none">Really cool book. Wasn't sure where it was going for a while but in a good way, and it ended cool. Kinda sad in parts, but definitely keeps your interest. If people in the world are really like this in therapy, that's kinda creepy. Highly recommended. </span>
